Start the machine via docker compose (call build.sh) and it outputs a tarball, that contains:

- ~/.vimrc
- ~/.vim
- ~/.vim-install-deps

This can be included via
tar xfz marcvim.tar ~

Execute .vim-install-deps on first run

On docker machines add following dependecies


RUN apt-get install -y ctags nodejs
RUN update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/node node /usr/bin/nodejs 10
RUN npm install -g jshint
# silver surfer
USER root
RUN git clone --branch 0.30.0 https://github.com/ggreer/the_silver_searcher /tmp/ag1
WORKDIR /tmp/ag1
RUN ./build.sh
RUN make install
